title: Final Fantasy CC Ring Fates *FIX*
description:
You must have the Final Fantasy Crystal Chronicles USA version ROM already. Doesnt matter if it has been trimmed but otherwise must be unaltered.

Use the patch included and no more \"Thanks FOr Playing\" nag screens.

Tested over at gbatemp and verified works. I can validate it 100% works on DSTT cartridge with v1.08 firmware.

Thanks from Yuri & CHelinka
